Homepage: https://github.com/davidboulay/CosmicShot
Description: CleanShot-style screenshot capture & annotation for COSMIC/Wayland
 CosmicShot is a fast screenshot tool for the COSMIC desktop (Pop!_OS) and
 other wlroots-style Wayland compositors. It offers region, full-screen and
 per-app-window capture, an annotation editor (arrows, text, shapes, blur,
 highlight, crop), scrolling screenshots, a pinned floating preview, and a
 panel tray icon with a capture menu.
 .
 Requires the COSMIC screenshot backend (cosmic-screenshot), which ships with
 the COSMIC desktop, plus an AppIndicator library for the tray icon.

